com.nus.cool.core.io.writestore

Class MetaHashFieldWS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nus.cool.core.io.writestore.MetaHashFieldWS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Output, MetaFieldWS
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MetaUserFieldWS

    public class MetaHashFieldWS
extends java.lang.Object
implements MetaFieldWS
    Hash MetaField write store.

    Hash MetaField layout --------------------------------------- | finger codec | fingers | value data | ---------------------------------------

    if fieldType == AppId, we do NOT store values

    value data layout -------------------------------------------------- | #values | value codec | value offsets | values | --------------------------------------------------
